#include "MCFClass.h"

Detailed Description

Testing template class for Min Cost Flow Problem solvers deriving from MCFClass. It is a template deriving from Master and holding an object of class Slave (both deriving from MCFClass), that does whatever Master does but also does whatever Slave does. The output is that of Master.
